    "publication_date": "2009-10",
    "currency": "CAD_2006",
    "summary": "Four partial-harvest trials near Prince George, BC (2006–2007) covering motor-manual CTL, motor-manual full-tree, mechanized full-tree, and mechanized CTL systems. Each trial reported stocking metrics (MTDFP), trail coverage, and stump-to-landing costs."
  },
  "trials": [
